<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <div style="background-color: #1a73e8; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: white;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">Welcome to LOREM</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #1a73e8; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hey {{name}},</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">Thanks for joining LOREM, your new favorite spot for all things music! We're pumped to have you on board.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">To get started, please activate your account with the code below:</p>
            <div style="background-color: #f1f3f4; display: inline-block; padding: 15px 25px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #d93025; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 2px;">{{activationCode}}</div>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">Click the button below to head to LOREM and enter your code. Let’s get the music playing!</p>
            <a href="https://lorem.com/activate" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background-color: #1a73e8; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px;">Activate Your Account</a>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f1f3f4; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: #d93025;">♪</span> LOREM - Where Music Lives <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #d93025;">♪</span></p>
            <p style="margin: 0;">© 2025 LOREM. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>